	* hexl.c [MSDOS]: Use binary file modes for non-text side of pipe.
	(main): Use fclose to close file opened by fopen.

	* fakemail.c (main) [MSDOS]: Dummy stub just to make the file compile.

	* movemail.c [MSDOS]: #undef `access'.

